column2: 80 degrees F- sunny- slightly breezy- green slime on top of water.
Weather was partly cloudy- 75 F- light breeze. lake is weedy and green.

column1: Earlier and heavier weed growth than I have seen in the last 5 years- particularly on a line from the south end of the mouth of the Red Cedar that almost reaches completely across the lake from west to east. Northwest end of lake also quite thick.
